           move      p-edt                to   w-all-str-cat (2)      .
           move      "'"                  to   w-all-str-cat (3)      .
           perform   all-str-cat-000      thru all-str-cat-999        .
           move      w-all-str-alf        to   w-exe-ttd-cow          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
